HEADWORD: life-sustaining
<hw>life-sustaining</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>being the seat or source
of life; performing a necessary function in the living body; <as>as, the
need for <ex>life-sustaining</ex> air and water</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> vital.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

